			</node>
		<node ID="ID_370187259" LINK="http://powerandsamplesize.com/Calculators/" TEXT="Power and Sample Size Calculators | HyLown">
			<node ID="ID_1233897901" TEXT="Welcome to the calculators home page of PowerAndSampleSize.com! Not much to go over here. Our calculators are pretty self-explanatory. At the top of each calculators page youll find a form and a graph. Enter values in the form then you can examine the graph to learn how sensitive the required sample size is to the input values youve provided" />
